PrecisEnactment of the CANADIAN FORCES OVERSEAS SCHOOLS REGULATIONS which replace an Order made in 1975 with features such as text in both official languages, modern terminology, updated cross-references to the Act and more precision in the area of teachers' entitlements to certain benefits.
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the CANADIAN FORCES OVERSEAS SCHOOLS REGULATIONS which replace
an Order made in 1975 with features such as text in both official
languages, modern terminology, updated cross-references to the Act and more
precision in the area of teachers' entitlements to certain benefits.
